==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: fifty-fifty
<hw>fifty-fifty</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a lottery in which the
organizers retain fifty percent of the money wagered, and distribute
fifty percent of the wagered money to the winner.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fig</ent>⟦br⟧
